<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>164</hymn_number>
<author>Rova</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A khawkna zen e maw, aw ka Lal Hukdampa,
 Kalvari tang lam him lungin ka gel thei puoi,
 Khawvel nasepnan ka na dim zawh tak ziekin.

[V2]
 Aw, lunggil nin tehaw, bangtin ka pui thei dem?
 Na lautha pang loin,
 Thapham vangkhuo zuonin,
 Thihnan a pui mang zo.

[V3]
 2. Na thisan tui bang luonna mun hun hetsak in,
 Thihna saudai sunga nga bang lengdente hi;
 La'n bang hun kiheisak kitin van Lal nunnem.

[V4]
 3. Lalpa kawma I tun phat leh bang I gen dem?
 Lautha mangte Lalpa kawma I puih loh chun;
 Van Lalmang Lal nunnem kawmah bang I gen dem?

[V5]
 4. Zinmang tui bang tawmin a gam pak bang tuoi leh,
 Nam liengvaite kipahnan hung dim tau un tin;
 Na gam ninnuom ah laituol nga bang leng tanau.</lyrics>
<title>Lunggila Nin Tehaw</title>
</song>